        "synopsis": {
            "value": "After being dumped by her ex-boyfriend on their six-year anniversary, Sayama Miyabi immerses herself into her job on the sales team at a real estate firm. Meanwhile, Donose Tsukasa, a highly successful company CEO, seeks a marriage of convenience to satisfy societal expectations.\n\nWhen he meets Miyabi, he proposes a “business marriage” where she can live rent-free in a luxury apartment, and he can present a “wife\" to the world. There’s just\n\none clause: If they develop genuine romantic emotions, they must divorce. However, cupid has other plans, and their arrangement begins to falter as emotions come into play.",
